Package: figaro
Title: Interactive Scientific Figure Composer
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Yuval", "Bloch", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = ""),
    person("Kesem", "Abramov", role = "aut", email = "kesemk@post.bgu.ac.il"),
    person("Nathan", "Edelman", role = "aut"))
Description: Opens the Figaro interactive figure composer in a local browser,
    pre-loaded with data frames, ggplot2 plot objects, or image files supplied
    from the R session. Simple ggplot2 objects are extracted as fully editable
    Figaro plots; complex plots and base-R graphics are rasterized and inserted
    as image panels.
